<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77d364e6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460aa–11"><num value="460aa–11">§ 460aa–11.</num><heading> Patents; restriction on issuance</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Patents shall not hereafter be issued for locations and claims heretofore made in the recreation area under the mining laws of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77d364e7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/92/400/s12">Pub. L. 92–400, § 12</ref>, <date date="1972-08-22">Aug. 22, 1972</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/86/615">86 Stat. 615</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
